title: KWASU GETS STRICT ON ACADEMIC PERFORMANCE As STUDENTS WITH LOW CGPA BEING WITHDRAWN!
date: 2025-10-03

The management of Kwara State University (KWASU) is no longer taking academic performance lightly. Students are strongly advised to take their academic standing seriously, as the institution has begun withdrawing students with low CGPA. This development emphasizes the need for students to stay above the minimum academic requirements to remain in their respective programs.  Be informed and monitor your PORTAL as more details shortly.
